	15. ``Drop Dead Gorgeous,'' New Line, $1.8 million, 1,207  
locations, $1,464 average, $8 million, two weeks. 
</P>
<P>
	16. ``Arlington Road,'' Sony, $1.3 million, 861 locations,  
$1,551 average, $22.2 million, four weeks. 
</P>
<P>
	17. ``Austin Powers: The Spy Who Shagged Me,'' New Line, $1.2  
million, 1,056 locations, $1,166 average, $198 million, eight 
weeks. 
</P>
<P>
	18. ``South Park: Bigger, Longer &AMP; Uncut,'' Paramount, $902,000,  
932 locations, $968 average, $49.9 million, five weeks. 
</P>
