<HEADLINE> 'Runaway Bride' Debuts at $35.1M / Box Office  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LOS ANGELES (AP) -- Julia Roberts and Richard Gere's reunion  
lovefest ``Runaway Bride'' ran away with the record for a romantic 
comedy debut and outpaced a trio of horror films over the weekend. 
</P>
<P>
	``Runaway Bride'' led the box office with $35.1 million, easily  
beating the scary ``The Blair Witch Project,'' the shark-infested 
