	Tim McGraw Leads CMA Nominations  
</P>
<P>
	NASHVILLE, Tenn. (AP) -- Tim McGraw was nominated for seven  
Country Music Association awards today, and will compete with 1998 
winner Garth Brooks for the top award of best entertainer. Other 
nominees for best entertainer were George Strait, Shania Twain and 
the Dixie Chicks. 

</P>
<P>
